+!***********************************************************************
+!                                                                      *
+      LOGICAL FUNCTION EQDBLE (DBLE1, DBLE2)
+!                                                                      *
+!***********************************************************************
+!
+      USE OCPCOMM4
+!
+      IMPLICIT NONE
+!
+!
+!   --|-----------------------------------------------------------|--
+!     | Delft University of Technology                            |
+!     | Faculty of Civil Engineering                              |
+!     | Environmental Fluid Mechanics Section                     |
+!     | P.O. Box 5048, 2600 GA  Delft, The Netherlands            |
+!     |                                                           |
+!     | Programmers: The SWAN team                                |
+!   --|-----------------------------------------------------------|--
+!
